Cs_snowed_in

I have decided to release it as a MiP for anyone who wants to check it out. It's fairly close to the actual office map so anything in that map is pretty much in here. (Theme wise, the layout is much different.)

UPDATE: 27/06/09

  • Made tons of changes to brushwork to make it look cleaner.
  • Applied "nodraw" to many missed textures that appeared outside of the map.

Note: To open this map in hammer, extract the .rar's contents into the "mapsrc" folder. (C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps(account name)\sourcesdk_content\cstrike\mapsrc)
